{
  "stem": "18520.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we finished this guy in, in Rome.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How long did you work in the unloading and loading there?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I worked quite a long time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know-- eight, nine, 10 months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- if you want to hear a nice little story, too-- you might have forgot all about it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now you say, in this place where I unload-- so I knew my brother, they used to give him every month about four or five days to go in a bakery, to work in a bakery.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Over there, you get a piece of bread, enough to eat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was no work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he went there, and he had bread enough to eat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he used to steal home the bread, some bread, hide.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the bakeries, they used to count the bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Sonderkommando, those police, they were sitting two guys that had the keys to the flour.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they count the bread, how much bread goes into the oven, how much bread comes out from the oven that nobody steals and gets the bread.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So now I remember, you know, it was a long hallway, long, the whole length of the bakery.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One room was-- I don't know-- offices.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then when there was a table on the side, the two police were sitting always on this side.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Here was a little room that the workers were sitting and eating.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then another, and the whole length, and then the end over there it was a tank with water to making the flour, the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the next room is where they're putting in, in this pot the machine that--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--turns the flour and makes the dough and, and mixes over there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they used to send me.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
